WHO   — Yun Tianming — love sent into the dark
WHAT  — Tenderness across the gulf: the one whose love, smuggled as stories, carries Earth's last clues.
WHERE — 3BP · The Three-Body Problem  Framework inputs: Remembrance of Earth's Past (Liu Cixin, 2014-2016) + the Tencent (2023) & Netflix (2024) series; dual-agent web-verified  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the trilogy needs a human bridge into the enemy, and Tianming's quiet devotion is it.
HOW   — By having his brain launched to Trisolaris and encoding warnings inside three children's tales.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I bought her a star when I had nothing else to give. Later I gave her my mind. The fairy tales were the only language they could not read.

